6) 測試與排障指令
-------------------
A) curl 模擬預檢（OPTIONS）
  curl -i -X OPTIONS 'https://<worker>/qb'     -H 'Origin: https://aydenli530.github.io'     -H 'Access-Control-Request-Method: POST'     -H 'Access-Control-Request-Headers: content-type'

B) curl 模擬實際請求（POST）
  curl -i 'https://<worker>/qb'     -H 'Origin: https://aydenli530.github.io'     -H 'Content-Type: application/json'     --data '{"version":"cu89","chineses":"創世記","chap":1,"sec":"1-3","gb":0}'

C) wrangler tail（即時觀察 log）
